    <p>External links are shown with a visible click counter. Incoming and outgoing links to other topics are displayed next to each post.</p>
  </td>
</tr>
<tr>
  <td class="feature">
    <span>Polls</span>
    <p>Create quick poll topics for the community to vote on.</p>
  </td>
  <td class="feature">
    <span>Spoilers</span>
    <p>Tags that blur potential spoilers, revealing only on click or tap.</p>
  </td>
</tr>
<tr>
  <td class="feature">
    <span>Flexible Formatting</span>
