  </td>
  <td class="feature">
    <span>Emoji</span>
    <p>Just start typing : and you have access to the
      complete list of <a href="http://www.emoji-cheat-sheet.com/">standard emoji</a>.
    </p>
  </td>
</tr>
<tr>
  <td class="feature">
    <span>Comprehensive API</span>
    <p>Anything you see on screen, you can also do via an API call. Discourse itself is a JavaScript app that talks to our API.</p>
  </td>
  <td class="feature">
    <span>Local Avatars</span>
    <p>Built-in local avatar generation with no external dependencies. Alternately, select an existing Gravatar, or upload a custom avatar.</p>
  </td>
</tr>
<tr>
  <td class="feature">
    <span>Email Invitations</span>
